resources.string: .1 Service Fee/Service charges / fee vary depending upon the type / category of CNIC.
.2 Delivery Time Service delivery time depends upon the service category; 1. Normal = 45 Days (Maximum) 2. Urgent = 30 Days (Maximum) 3. Executive = 12 Days (Maximum)
.3 Issuance Authority CNIC will be issued by the NADRA.
.4 Fee Payment Mode Fee payment mode is cash only and will be collected at NADRA counters.

• 1 Service Fee Computerized Certificate Issuance Fee is Rs. 100

 • 2 Delivery Time For Copy Service Time at institute for Delivery of Copy within 60 days of birth 3 working days and in case of delay registration 61st to 7 years 7 working days.

 • 3 Delivery Time For Original Certificate Service Time for Delivery of Original Certificate through Post within 60 Days of Birth 7 working days and incase of delay registration 61st-7 years 11 working days.

 • 4 Issuance Authority This service will be issued by Secretary Union Council for birth within 60 days or Administrator / Nazim UC incase of delayed registration from 61st day to 7 years.

 • 5 Fee Payment Mode Payment should be Cash and in Pakistan Rupees (PKR).

 • 6 Designated Bank (Adjacent to institute)
